Translations.Text: Et caravan arrived their patris dictus ego sense smell Joseph. someone enlighten me
They dictus DEUS vos est adhuc tuus veteris confusion
When bearer bonus news arrived he threw shirt his face whereupon his vision restored He dictus ego non tell vos ego knew DEUS quod vos non know
They dictus Noster patris pray noster forgiveness; nos est wrong indeed
He dictus ego implore my Dominus forgive vos; He est Forgiver Merciful
When they iniit Joseph's quarters he embraced his parentes dictus Welcome to Egypt! DEUS testimentum VOS est safe HIC

He levabat his parentes throne They fell prostrate ante eum. He dictus O my patris hoc est fulfillment my veteris dream My Dominus factus it advenit true He beatus me delivered me prison brought vos ex desert post devil driven wedge me my frater! My Dominus est Generis towards whomever He testimentum. He est Knower the Multus Wise

My Dominus Vos dedit me kingship taught me interpretation de dreams Initiator de caelum terra; Vos est my Dominus Magister in hoc vita Hereafter Let me abiit prout submitter comes me cum the righteous
(Hoc est news preter nos reveal vos. Vos est presentis when they factus their unanimous decision throw Joseph bene) prout they conspired unus
Multus people non matter quod vos non believe
Vos non asking them any moneta; vos simply deliver hoc reminder totus people
